snippet.title: Backrooms Cleanup Crew Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Backrooms Cleanup Crew on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3140990/Backrooms_Cleanup_Crew/

Backrooms Cleanup Crew is an upcoming game on Steam where you and your crew are tasked with cleaning up after the last exploration team's ill-fated journey into the Backrooms. Dodge and wash your way through deadly incursions and leave no trace.

Trailer Music Attribution:
'The Encounter' by Scott Buckley - released under CC-BY 4.0. www.scottbuckley.com.au
